The paper deals with path planning and control of a mobile robot, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of a potential field approach and control signal also suggests a systems and control (cs.SY) aspect to the paper. The paper also involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which could place it under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves simulation results, which could suggest a machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV) aspect to the paper.
